official_title: To require the Secretary of the Treasury to mint coins in commemoration of the Women in Military Service for America Memorial.
short_title: Women in Military Service for America Memorial Commemorative Coin Act

summary.text: Women in Military Service for America Memorial Commemorative Coin Act - Directs the Secretary of the Treasury to issue five-dollar gold coins and one-dollar silver coins symbolic of women's service in the armed forces.
